  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until pink and cooked through.",
    "Remove the shrimp from the skillet and set aside.",
    "In the same skillet, add the smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chopped scallions and cook for 1 minute, until they start to soften.",
    "Add the cooked rice to the skillet and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes, until heated through.",
    "Add the cooked shrimp back into the skillet and stir-fry for 1 minute, until combined with the rice.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and crispy bacon.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the crispy fried rice to a serving platter and garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
  ],
